1
00:00:06,060 --> 00:00:08,340
♪The white sail came too late♪

2
00:00:09,100 --> 00:00:11,340
♪Where did he go?♪

3
00:00:12,340 --> 00:00:13,820
♪Snow veils the mountains♪

4
00:00:14,060 --> 00:00:16,340
♪Love endures beyond life and death♪

5
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:19,580
♪A black chess piece♪

6
00:00:19,660 --> 00:00:23,140
♪Whose game did he stumble into?♪

7
00:00:23,740 --> 00:00:27,620
♪All his life, there's no escape♪

8
00:00:29,420 --> 00:00:33,340
♪In ten thousand years, what will still remain?♪

9
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:40,020
♪Will anyone still love with an unchanging heart?♪

10
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:42,620
♪I will remember♪

11
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:46,660
♪Those days long past♪

12
00:00:47,660 --> 00:00:51,580
♪As the wind drifts with the white sail♪

13
00:00:52,220 --> 00:00:53,660
♪Ten thousand years ago♪

14
00:00:53,780 --> 00:00:57,500
♪Did you once walk this shore?♪

15
00:00:57,740 --> 00:01:02,940
♪Why can't our bond be severed in this life?♪

16
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:05,100
♪I am lost yet willing♪

17
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:09,580
♪Still I love you with a steadfast heart♪

18
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:17,100
♪Until all things fade away♪

19
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:27,220
♪The stars will remember us♪

20
00:01:27,220 --> 00:01:28,220
[Love & Crown]

21
00:01:28,220 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from the novel "My Queen" by Xie Lounan]

22
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 23]

23
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,260
Madam.

24
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,020
You cannot hold your drink.

25
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:52,930
Do not drink any more.

26
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,020
Yet he said

27
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,410
she was the finest blessing he ever gained.

28
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:09,850
So this is it.

29
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:13,290
I was never anything at all.

30
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,570
Madam,

31
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:17,170
you are truly drunk.

32
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,500
Let me take you back to rest.

33
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,100
Madam.

34
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,450
When I was a child,

35
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,570
there were days so bitter I could hardly breathe,

36
00:02:57,190 --> 00:02:59,060
moments when I thought I could not go on.

37
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,940
So I found a place

38
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:09,730
and hid myself away.

39
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:19,410
I hid for a long time,

40
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,060
until

41
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,060
he appeared.

42
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:31,380
He took my hand

43
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:34,010
and told me not to fear.

44
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:13,340
You have been the light of my life.

45
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:19,250
I have lived my whole life for you.

46
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,540
Once, I wished to ask you:

47
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:24,260
back then, did you truly mean to save me,

48
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:26,460
or was I merely a piece on your board?

49
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:28,850
Did you want me to believe

50
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:32,810
that I owed you my life?

51
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,580
But tell me,

52
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:40,170
do I truly owe you anything?

53
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,540
Do I truly owe you anything?

54
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,810
Xiao Huan, do I truly owe you anything?

55
00:04:45,390 --> 00:04:46,100
Madam.

56
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,220
Madam,

57
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:49,100
you are truly drunk.

58
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:50,850
Madam.

59
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:53,700
I no longer care.

60
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:54,730
Because

61
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:57,020
the man who defiled my mother

62
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,220
held an identity so exalted

63
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,900
she could never speak it aloud.

64
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,820
They all said my mother was wanton,

65
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:05,520
that she betrayed the late Emperor's trust.

66
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,700
They tied her to a stake

67
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:11,900
and burned her alive.

68
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,660
But whom did she truly betray?

69
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:15,950
[Let me bear the heir of His Majesty]

70
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:17,580
My mother wrote a letter in her own blood.

71
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,490
By then, the late Emperor was gone.

72
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,610
Everyone wanted her dead.

73
00:05:34,190 --> 00:05:36,850
So she wrote this blood letter

74
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:38,610
to prove who I was,

75
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,780
hoping I might live to grow up safely.

76
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,980
But she never knew

77
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:46,250
that my identity would be concealed.

78
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:50,900
It was you all

79
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:53,290
who ruined my mother,

80
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:55,660
ruined me,

81
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:58,100
and left us unable to speak a word.

82
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,780
What a fine imperial family.

83
00:06:03,390 --> 00:06:05,410
Such overwhelming majesty you wield.

84
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:07,850
Madam,

85
00:06:08,430 --> 00:06:09,930
you must not say another word.

86
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,170
Then tell me,

87
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:22,370
what right do you have to pretend to be the righteous one?

88
00:06:24,390 --> 00:06:27,170
Why did you deceive me for more than ten years,

89
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,730
and make me give everything,

90
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:30,930
pouring my whole life into repaying you?

91
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:33,490
I am a princess as well.

92
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,020
What you are entitled to,

93
00:06:38,070 --> 00:06:39,540
I am entitled to as well.

94
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,930
Speak.

95
00:06:43,190 --> 00:06:43,980
Xiao Huan,

96
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:46,460
say something.

97
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:49,610
Can you not rise and say at least one word?

98
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:50,900
Madam,

99
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,290
what is it you want me to say?

100
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:05,100
You are right.

101
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,850
No matter what you say,

102
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:12,100
there is no path back for us.

103
00:07:15,070 --> 00:07:16,370
Aside from hating you,

104
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:20,610
I have no other road left to walk.

105
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:34,340
Xiao Huan,

106
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,340
for my mother's death,

107
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:42,250
I will have your Xiao clan repay it.

108
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:53,180
[Yaoqing Hall]

109
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,020
Your Majesty, Your Majesty the Empress,

110
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:27,980
Vice Commander Lu

111
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,980
has safely escorted the Imperial Father-in-law to Fayun Temple

112
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:31,290
and settled him at Deer Courtyard.

113
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:32,940
Good.

114
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,770
See to his daily needs with utmost care,

115
00:08:35,910 --> 00:08:37,890
and let no one else disturb him.

116
00:08:38,550 --> 00:08:39,340
Yes.

117
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,460
My thanks, Your Majesty.

118
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,580
I only hope my father,

119
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:50,180
while living in seclusion,

120
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,460
may come to understand things clearly.

121
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,220
In due time,

122
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,580
when all has settled,

123
00:08:55,670 --> 00:08:57,010
you may still visit him.

124
00:08:57,390 --> 00:08:58,300
Deer Courtyard is not far.

125
00:09:30,750 --> 00:09:31,580
What do you mean?

126
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:34,530
Yesterday I overheard something I should not have heard.

127
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,650
But rest assured, Madam.

128
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:41,060
I have already checked the area.

129
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,340
There were no other palace servants present.

130
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:51,180
You are to keep my secret forever,

131
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,300
and yet why

132
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,340
did you not kill yourself?

133
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:06,180
Wait!

134
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,370
Though there may be some measure of performance to it,

135
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:16,300
I am quite fond of this way

136
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,100
of showing loyalty.

137
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,220
Death will not be needed.

138
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:34,980
I called you here,

139
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:37,340
and drank myself senseless before you,

140
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,820
because I had already decided.

141
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:43,890
You are someone I can trust.

142
00:10:49,390 --> 00:10:51,730
I have studied the art of reading hearts with His Majesty for years.

143
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,250
A person's eyes

144
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,850
never lie.

145
00:10:58,750 --> 00:11:00,370
Your eyes tell me

146
00:11:01,790 --> 00:11:03,250
you would live for me,

147
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:04,580
and die for me.

148
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:07,180
But what of it?

149
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:09,850
In the end, you will never obtain

150
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,100
my heart.

151
00:11:22,270 --> 00:11:23,650
To die for the Imperial Preceptor

152
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,770
would be my greatest honor.

153
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,250
I do not want you dead.

154
00:11:39,030 --> 00:11:40,370
I want you

155
00:11:41,510 --> 00:11:42,940
to live well for my sake.

156
00:11:52,750 --> 00:11:53,530
Your Majesty,

157
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,010
Your Majesty the Empress,

158
00:11:57,630 --> 00:11:58,850
the Imperial Preceptor seeks audience.

159
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,530
See to your duties first.

160
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,420
I shall take my leave.

161
00:12:29,270 --> 00:12:30,650
[Wuying Hall]
Your Majesty, blessings upon you.

162
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:35,420
Are you bringing medicine for His Majesty?

163
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,250
Indeed.

164
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:40,340
His Majesty's foundation was gravely injured before,

165
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,700
and requires careful nurturing.

166
00:12:46,270 --> 00:12:47,300
It has been some time.

167
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:49,180
You have grown much thinner.

168
00:12:50,390 --> 00:12:51,610
Your Highness is radiant,

169
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,180
your elegance outshining pearls and jade.

170
00:12:53,630 --> 00:12:55,340
I can only feel ashamed in your presence.

171
00:12:56,870 --> 00:12:58,100
His Majesty awaits inside the hall.

172
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:58,940
Please proceed.

173
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:01,940
I respectfully see Your Highness off.

174
00:13:12,220 --> 00:13:14,670
[Pure and Spotless]

175
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,460
Imperial Preceptor Du,

176
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,650
it has been quite some time.

177
00:13:16,910 --> 00:13:17,700
Indeed.

178
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,490
I have not stepped into Wuying Hall

179
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:21,460
for one hundred and seventeen days.

180
00:13:24,270 --> 00:13:27,220
Why do you come personally today to deliver the medicine?

181
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,580
I have come first to deliver the medicine,

182
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:42,890
and second to report to Your Majesty

183
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,530
that I have thought things through.

184
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:47,300
Thought through what?

185
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:48,730
I acknowledge my faults.

186
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:51,250
What fault do you speak of?

187
00:13:51,670 --> 00:13:52,580
My fault

188
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,180
lies in overstepping,

189
00:13:54,390 --> 00:13:55,300
in lacking restraint,

190
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,370
and knowing no limits.

191
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:58,250
Matters between Your Majesty and Her Majesty

192
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,940
are, in the end, your household affairs.

193
00:14:00,510 --> 00:14:01,850
Your Majesty is the Son of Heaven.

194
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:04,300
Though Your Majesty bears the world in your heart,

195
00:14:04,790 --> 00:14:06,530
you are still flesh and blood.

196
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:11,100
As for the Jiangzhou matter,

197
00:14:11,870 --> 00:14:13,250
it was my narrow-mindedness.

198
00:14:15,390 --> 00:14:16,650
You overstate it.

199
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:20,180
I should not have failed Your Majesty's earnest expectations,

200
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:22,700
nor betrayed Your Majesty's trust.

201
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,100
Henceforth,

202
00:14:24,670 --> 00:14:26,300
I shall abide strictly by my station,

203
00:14:26,870 --> 00:14:29,060
and never again presume to judge Your Majesty's family affairs.

204
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:33,100
In my eyes,

205
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:36,580
your sincerity matters more than your remorse.

206
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:38,490
If it is sincerity His Majesty desires,

207
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,180
I have brought it.

208
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:43,490
Attend me.

209
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:44,250
Present it.

210
00:15:01,260 --> 00:15:02,300
[Great Qi Waterworks Map]

211
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:08,180
A waterworks map.

212
00:15:09,100 --> 00:15:10,460
You are indeed talented.

213
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:12,370
Late summer and early autumn in our dynasty

214
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:13,530
often bring heavy floods.

215
00:15:14,030 --> 00:15:16,650
Even this year's locust plague is tied to the flooding.

216
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:20,530
I specially drafted this waterworks map

217
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:22,940
for the Ministry of Works to examine.

218
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:32,300
You even recorded the tides of each passing year.

219
00:15:32,630 --> 00:15:33,700
You have been most diligent.

220
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:39,770
Such matters should be addressed sooner rather than later.

221
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,850
Tell me, what do this year's celestial signs reveal?

222
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:43,060
Can we begin the works?

223
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:47,300
I thank Your Majesty for granting me another chance.

224
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:50,180
I shall not disappoint Your Majesty.

225
00:15:51,630 --> 00:15:52,810
In my heart,

226
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:55,100
Du Tingxin will always be Du Tingxin,

227
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:57,170
meticulous in all you do.

228
00:16:03,310 --> 00:16:04,770
Your Majesty speaks truly.

229
00:16:05,830 --> 00:16:07,140
Whatever I set my mind to

230
00:16:07,920 --> 00:16:09,500
is always done with utmost precision.

231
00:16:14,980 --> 00:16:18,660
[Great Qi Waterworks Map]

232
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:22,040
[Shutong Hall]

233
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:22,900
Ying, look.

234
00:16:23,670 --> 00:16:25,020
I have prepared something for you.

235
00:16:25,310 --> 00:16:26,380
Your favorite dish.

236
00:16:26,640 --> 00:16:27,260
Come.

237
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:29,900
Do not just stand there.

238
00:16:29,920 --> 00:16:30,690
Eat while it is warm.

239
00:16:32,030 --> 00:16:32,530
Qianqing,

240
00:16:32,710 --> 00:16:33,860
tell me, are women with child

241
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:35,260
often without appetite,

242
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:37,290
unable to stomach food or tea,

243
00:16:37,830 --> 00:16:39,380
and sleepless night after night?

244
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:41,140
It is possible.

245
00:16:44,590 --> 00:16:45,380
Ying,

246
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:46,980
why do you ask such a thing?

247
00:16:56,950 --> 00:16:57,740
Qianqing,

248
00:16:57,920 --> 00:16:59,170
I am with child.

249
00:17:03,550 --> 00:17:04,820
What... What did you say?

250
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,170
Whose is it?

251
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:17,650
Your Highness, you must not enter.

252
00:17:17,670 --> 00:17:18,170
Your Highness!

253
00:17:22,670 --> 00:17:23,450
Your Highness.

254
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:25,860
You beast!

255
00:17:25,990 --> 00:17:26,730
I will kill you!

256
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:27,650
Stop!

257
00:17:27,990 --> 00:17:29,730
You storm Wuying Hall without cause.

258
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:30,650
Xiao Qianqing.

259
00:17:30,800 --> 00:17:32,820
You had best give me one reason not to punish you.

260
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:40,900
Feng Wufu,

261
00:17:41,470 --> 00:17:42,300
step out first.

262
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:43,210
Close the doors.

263
00:17:45,430 --> 00:17:46,410
Go on.

264
00:17:46,430 --> 00:17:47,210
Yes.

265
00:17:56,120 --> 00:17:57,580
Ying is innocent of the world.

266
00:17:57,800 --> 00:17:59,860
This scoundrel dares bully her,

267
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:00,650
making her...

268
00:18:02,670 --> 00:18:03,970
Making her with child.

269
00:18:05,320 --> 00:18:06,300
Impossible!

270
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:07,900
I have remained pure with the Princess.

271
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,010
How could she be with child?

272
00:18:09,030 --> 00:18:10,010
You dare deny it?

273
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:10,970
She told me herself.

274
00:18:10,990 --> 00:18:12,100
If not you, then who else?

275
00:18:12,670 --> 00:18:14,010
- You must have taken advantage while... - Enough.

276
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:18,210
Li Hongqing is not such a man.

277
00:18:18,230 --> 00:18:19,690
Ying spoke it herself.

278
00:18:19,710 --> 00:18:21,620
She is simple and honest by nature.

279
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:22,820
She would not lie.

280
00:18:26,950 --> 00:18:28,010
If such a thing is true,

281
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:30,210
I am willing to offer my head.

282
00:18:40,260 --> 00:18:42,420
[Shutong Hall]

283
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,010
Ying.

284
00:19:12,670 --> 00:19:13,210
Ying.

285
00:19:14,030 --> 00:19:14,690
How is it?

286
