339
00:23:25,560 --> 00:23:26,340
Zhong Lin?

340
00:23:26,920 --> 00:23:27,730
Zhong Lin.

341
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:28,690
Zhong Lin.

342
00:23:30,030 --> 00:23:30,620
Zhong Lin,

343
00:23:30,620 --> 00:23:31,250
