So you were hiding here.

346
00:23:37,530 --> 00:23:38,580
Why did you come?

347
00:23:39,670 --> 00:23:40,730
You still dare ask?

348
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:45,490
You shared my bed, and now you start avoiding me.

349
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:48,010
If I hadn't come looking for you,

350
00:23:48,190 --> 00:23:49,450
would you really never have come to me, even till death?

351
00:23:49,470 --> 00:23:50,490
What nonsense is that?

352
00:23:50,510 --> 00:23:51,410
Who shared a bed with you?

353
00:23:51,430 --> 00:23:52,620
I was drunk.

354
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:53,900
I remember nothing.

355
00:23:54,990 --> 00:23:55,930
Fine.

356
00:23:55,930 --> 00:23:57,410
