375
00:24:49,240 --> 00:24:50,460
It is the Nanyi venom-scorpion.

376
00:24:51,350 --> 00:24:53,010
Fortunately, its venom is not fatal.

377
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:56,490
But its venom will cause hallucinations.

378
00:24:58,070 --> 00:24:59,290
- Hallucinations? - Enough.

379
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,530
I will take you to sit up ahead.

380
00:25:01,550 --> 00:25:02,180
Come.

381
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:04,330
Zhong Lin...

382
00:25:04,590 --> 00:25:05,220
Zhong Lin.

383
00:25:06,510 --> 00:25:07,140
Zhong Lin,

384
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:08,660
I like you.

385
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:09,460
I...

386
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,530
I want to marry you.

387
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:17,620
So fast.

388
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:20,490
This venom truly works well.

389
00:25:20,790 --> 00:25:21,770
Tell me,

390
00:25:22,350 --> 00:25:23,700
do you like me too?

391
00:25:23,720 --> 00:25:24,490
Do you?

392
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:26,940
- Do you? - Yes.

393
00:25:26,960 --> 00:25:28,220
- Do you? - Yes.

394
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:29,010
Yes.

395
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:31,660
I knew you liked me too.

396
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:34,380
You would never abandon me.

397
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,180
Right.

398
00:25:35,590 --> 00:25:36,940
I will not abandon you.

399
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:41,180
And then?

400
00:25:41,750 --> 00:25:42,530
That is all.

401
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:56,570
You are unharmed.

402
00:25:58,480 --> 00:25:58,980
I...

403
00:25:59,590 --> 00:26:01,050
I was never bitten at all.

404
00:26:01,790 --> 00:26:02,220
You...

405
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:05,620
But everything I said just now was true.

406
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,140
Are you mad?

407
00:26:07,740 --> 00:26:08,330
Zhong Lin,

408
00:26:08,350 --> 00:26:09,120
I am not mad.

409
00:26:09,120 --> 00:26:10,560
I like you. I wish to marry you.

410
00:26:11,510 --> 00:26:12,730
You admitted it just now.

411
00:26:12,750 --> 00:26:13,810
You like me too.

412
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:15,220
You cannot deny it.

413
00:26:16,310 --> 00:26:18,090
Do you know what kind of person I am?

414
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:19,570
Of course I know.

415
00:26:23,880 --> 00:26:24,700
You saw it.

416
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:25,900
I have survived

417
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:27,900
only by these crooked tricks.

418
00:26:28,830 --> 00:26:30,420
Because I am of the Lingbi Sect.

419
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:32,420
So, Your Highness,

420
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:34,330
please do not make such senseless jokes again.

421
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:36,620
I do not like it.

422
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:38,620
I was not jesting.

423
00:26:43,550 --> 00:26:44,770
I was sincere.

424
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:49,460
You have already feigned death

425
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:50,900
