426
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:53,620
You are now under my protection.

427
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:05,900
It is useless.

428
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:10,660
From the day I joined the Lingbi Sect,

429
00:27:11,750 --> 00:27:13,290
