433
00:27:20,030 --> 00:27:21,640
I have tried hundreds

434
00:27:21,850 --> 00:27:23,090
of antidotes.

435
00:27:23,960 --> 00:27:25,890
But this poison has no cure at all.

436
00:27:34,030 --> 00:27:35,290
So, Xiao Qianqing,

437
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:40,010
I will live my entire life in fear.

438
00:27:40,590 --> 00:27:41,660
Startled at the slightest sound,

439
00:27:42,510 --> 00:27:43,700
haunted by shadows,

440
00:27:45,070 --> 00:27:47,140
even the sound of a copper bell terrifies me,

441
00:27:47,160 --> 00:27:49,620
for fear the Heartbane may erupt.

442
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:56,860
This is the kind of person I am.

443
00:27:58,720 --> 00:27:59,980
Someone like me,

444
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:03,730
would you still marry?

445
00:28:21,370 --> 00:28:22,760
Do you truly feel nothing

446
00:28:23,070 --> 00:28:24,600
for Princess Ying?

447
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:27,090
