448
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:28,280
I would never be presumptuous.

449
00:28:28,280 --> 00:28:29,440
Set aside your terror.

450
00:28:30,030 --> 00:28:31,660
Set aside her rank as Princess.

451
00:28:32,180 --> 00:28:32,670
You,

452
00:28:32,860 --> 00:28:33,720
Li Hongqing,

453
00:28:34,110 --> 00:28:34,900
toward Xiao Ying,

454
00:28:35,310 --> 00:28:37,050
do you truly feel not even the slightest affection?

455
00:28:43,200 --> 00:28:45,730
