456
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:50,010
My sister

457
00:28:50,030 --> 00:28:51,140
has a willful temper.

458
00:28:51,550 --> 00:28:53,290
She loves and hates with extremity.

459
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:55,220
If you are uncertain,

460
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:56,980
you must not provoke her.

461
00:28:58,310 --> 00:28:59,940
But if you are certain,

462
00:29:00,310 --> 00:29:01,700
I have no objection.

463
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:03,220
I understand.

464
00:29:04,000 --> 00:29:04,810
For now,

465
00:29:05,350 --> 00:29:06,860
I will not see Princess Ying.

466
00:29:07,310 --> 00:29:08,810
Not until I am certain of myself.

467
00:29:11,110 --> 00:29:11,730
Good.

468
00:29:19,510 --> 00:29:20,080
Mother,

469
00:29:20,080 --> 00:29:21,700
