471
00:29:27,310 --> 00:29:29,220
On ordinary days you may fool around all you like,

472
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:32,380
but you must never marry Zhong Lin.

473
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,290
What if I insist?

474
00:29:49,110 --> 00:29:49,860
