477
00:30:14,550 --> 00:30:16,090
to witness your skill.

478
00:30:16,510 --> 00:30:17,940
Summoning me into the palace?

479
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:19,770
It is clearly a scheme.

480
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:27,570
My thanks for Her Majesty's favor.

481
00:30:28,720 --> 00:30:29,570
However,

482
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:32,010
