483
00:30:32,270 --> 00:30:35,010
I did not bring my beloved Sanhua Purple-Haired Brush.

484
00:30:35,310 --> 00:30:36,900
I shall return to retrieve it.

485
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:38,380
Sanhua Purple-Haired?

486
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:41,140
There is one here as well.

487
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:50,050
I have another quirk.

488
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:52,660
Before I put brush to paper,

489
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:55,530
I must drink two cups of the Sangluo Wine I brew myself.

490
00:30:55,550 --> 00:30:58,010
Unless Miss Zhong finishes copying these scriptures,

491
00:30:59,310 --> 00:31:01,530
this servant cannot allow you to leave.

492
00:31:10,510 --> 00:31:11,330
Good aunt,

493
00:31:12,550 --> 00:31:15,620
if the Prince of Yuzhang learns that I have gone missing,

494
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,620
he will certainly come seeking me.

495
00:31:18,790 --> 00:31:20,220
Can you bear the consequence?

496
00:31:23,720 --> 00:31:25,380
The Prince of Yuzhang

497
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:27,220
is taking supper with the Empress Dowager.

498
00:31:27,750 --> 00:31:29,490
He may remain in the palace tonight.

499
00:31:30,590 --> 00:31:31,700
I fear

500
00:31:32,510 --> 00:31:33,940
