508
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:11,620
It was this woman.

509
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:12,730
She seduced me!

510
00:33:15,510 --> 00:33:16,620
She is mine.

511
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,140
You dare touch her?

512
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:20,010
Qing,

513
00:33:20,750 --> 00:33:21,770
this vile woman

514
00:33:22,240 --> 00:33:23,460
