515
00:33:23,510 --> 00:33:24,860
in my own chambers,

516
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:26,220
yet you defend her?

517
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:27,180
Mother,

518
00:33:28,720 --> 00:33:30,090
these palace ploys...

519
00:33:31,110 --> 00:33:33,140
Are you certain you wish to use them

520
00:33:33,270 --> 00:33:34,050
on your own son?

521
00:33:58,700 --> 00:34:01,780
[Wuying Hall]

522
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:07,530
I seek to marry Zhong Lin

523
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:09,610
and beg Your Majesty to grant the marriage.

524
00:34:12,300 --> 00:34:13,630
[Pure and Spotless]

525
00:34:13,630 --> 00:34:14,490
Xiao Qianqing,

526
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,860
have you gone mad?

527
00:34:17,110 --> 00:34:18,980
A woman of unknown origin,

528
00:34:19,030 --> 00:34:20,010
with her virtue

529
00:34:20,150 --> 00:34:21,170
in doubt.

530
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:23,820
You would make her your princess?

531
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:27,490
Mother speaks ill of Zhong Lin,

532
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:28,780
yet do you know

533
00:34:29,230 --> 00:34:31,210
that in the many times I was trapped,

534
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:32,900
my life hanging by a thread,

535
00:34:34,510 --> 00:34:36,130
it was she who risked everything

536
00:34:36,510 --> 00:34:37,570
again and again to save me.

537
00:34:38,590 --> 00:34:40,490
There are countless fine women in this world,

538
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:42,170
but in my heart,

539
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:44,740
none compare to Zhong Lin's courage and loyalty.

540
00:34:45,000 --> 00:34:46,050
Her devotion runs true.

541
00:34:51,030 --> 00:34:52,490
In this lifetime,

542
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:53,980
I will marry no one but her.

543
00:35:03,110 --> 00:35:05,490
I will never allow you to wed

544
00:35:06,070 --> 00:35:08,130
a lowborn girl of the martial world.

545
00:35:08,550 --> 00:35:09,610
Especially one

546
00:35:10,510 --> 00:35:11,900
versed in crooked and unorthodox ways.

547
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:13,570
She is not a maiden of proper lineage.

548
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,530
Put this thought out of your mind.

549
00:35:26,630 --> 00:35:28,210
The Empress Dowager speaks truly.

550
00:35:29,670 --> 00:35:31,210
