553
00:35:42,710 --> 00:35:44,780
But Zhong Lin's heart is upright,

554
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:47,360
and she journeyed a thousand li to resolve Xuzhou's plight.

555
00:35:48,190 --> 00:35:50,380
She also retrieved Frost Blossom with the Prince of Yuzhang,

556
00:35:50,750 --> 00:35:53,340
which counts as service in protecting the throne.

557
00:35:53,510 --> 00:35:54,610
She deserves a reward.

558
00:35:55,760 --> 00:35:56,690
Therefore,

559
00:35:57,110 --> 00:35:58,650
today I decree

560
00:35:59,190 --> 00:36:01,490
that Zhong Lin be granted the title Princess of Ding'an,

561
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:03,010
and this shall be proclaimed to all.

562
00:36:11,710 --> 00:36:12,490
Zhong Lin,

563
00:36:13,190 --> 00:36:14,170
from this day on,

564
00:36:14,280 --> 00:36:16,490
His Majesty and I are your family.

565
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:18,820
If anyone dares wrong you again,

566
00:36:19,190 --> 00:36:20,380
causing you grievance,

567
00:36:20,710 --> 00:36:22,530
we shall uphold justice for you.

568
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:25,490
I, Zhong Lin,

569
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:26,570
thank Your Majesty

570
00:36:26,590 --> 00:36:27,900
and Her Majesty the Empress.

571
00:36:32,150 --> 00:36:33,090
Rise.

572
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,130
Zhong Lin,

573
00:36:39,510 --> 00:36:41,340
as for you and the Prince of Yuzhang,

574
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:43,690
you need only follow your true heart.

575
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:44,780
I ask you,

576
00:36:45,710 --> 00:36:47,570
are you willing to marry the Prince of Yuzhang?

577
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:58,780
Your Majesty,

578
00:36:59,630 --> 00:37:00,490
I am willing.

579
00:37:00,780 --> 00:37:03,140
♪Her hairpin sways...♪

580
00:37:04,230 --> 00:37:05,010
Thank

581
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:06,570
Your Majesty for this marriage decree.

582
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:13,780
♪The warmth of your touch♪

583
00:37:14,180 --> 00:37:16,660
♪Turns time into a gentle circle♪

584
00:37:17,180 --> 00:37:20,860
♪Pear blossoms dream beneath the snow♪

585
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:25,140
♪Years turn and fade♪

586
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:27,420
♪Wax and wane♪

587
00:37:28,100 --> 00:37:32,220
♪Fate etched deep in every line of my hand♪

588
00:37:33,300 --> 00:37:35,780
♪Your eyes hold our garden of bloom♪

589
00:37:35,900 --> 00:37:38,540
♪Then sudden rain pours down♪

590
00:37:38,900 --> 00:37:42,700
♪Washing the sweetness from the pear petals♪

591
00:37:44,620 --> 00:37:48,660
♪Softly, slowly, round and clear, faint yet near♪

592
00:37:50,060 --> 00:37:54,260
♪A hairpin carved with a pure white vow♪

593
00:37:54,780 --> 00:37:57,260
♪Drifting, falling, endless and tender♪

594
00:37:57,500 --> 00:37:59,980
♪Through every season, every year, every day♪

595
00:38:00,740 --> 00:38:04,980
♪The scent of pear blossoms fills the garden again...♪

596
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,050
What is it?

597
00:38:09,550 --> 00:38:10,260
Zhong Lin.

598
00:38:11,110 --> 00:38:13,210
The marriage bestowed by His Majesty and Her Majesty,

599
00:38:13,550 --> 00:38:15,130
you agreed to it yourself.

600
00:38:15,230 --> 00:38:16,380
You are not allowed to go back on it.

601
00:38:17,260 --> 00:38:19,620
♪The evening breeze drifts softly♪

602
00:38:19,900 --> 00:38:21,900
♪Candle tears tremble lightly♪

603
00:38:22,580 --> 00:38:26,020
♪Falling upon the rouge upon my dressing table…♪

604
00:38:26,230 --> 00:38:27,170
Xiao Qianqing.

605
00:38:28,230 --> 00:38:30,010
Are you serious about me?

606
00:38:30,150 --> 00:38:30,940
Of course.

607
00:38:31,510 --> 00:38:32,570
You are not teasing you?

608
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,300
Then is it because you pity me?

609
00:38:37,230 --> 00:38:39,130
Otherwise I truly cannot understand.

610
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,900
You are the Prince of Yuzhang,

611
00:38:41,150 --> 00:38:42,010
noble in status,

612
00:38:42,030 --> 00:38:43,010
lacking in nothing.

613
00:38:43,030 --> 00:38:44,690
How could you possibly like someone like me?

614
00:38:44,710 --> 00:38:45,490
What's wrong with liking you?

615
00:38:49,980 --> 00:38:52,420
♪The letter from that year♪

616
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:54,820
♪Hidden inside its creases♪

617
00:38:55,540 --> 00:38:59,100
♪Is a spring not yet dried...♪

618
00:39:00,510 --> 00:39:01,260
Zhong Lin.

619
00:39:02,510 --> 00:39:03,300
I know.

620
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:07,010
You and I have both wandered without rest.

621
00:39:07,070 --> 00:39:08,780
But now that we have each other,

622
00:39:09,510 --> 00:39:12,340
our hearts can finally find peace for the future.

623
00:39:14,100 --> 00:39:16,580
♪Through every season, every year, every day♪

624
00:39:17,340 --> 00:39:20,740
♪The scent of pear blossoms fills the garden again...♪

625
00:39:20,760 --> 00:39:22,010
I do not care who you are.

626
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:24,380
I only want you to know

627
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:26,570
that to me, Xiao Qianqing,

628
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:28,130
you are the woman I love most.

629
00:39:31,070 --> 00:39:32,380
I like you.

630
00:39:33,150 --> 00:39:35,780
And I never once thought I would be able to marry you.

631
00:39:36,670 --> 00:39:38,380
I am truly very happy.

632
00:39:39,100 --> 00:39:43,060
♪The scent of pear blossoms fills the garden again♪

633
00:39:45,260 --> 00:39:49,460
♪Fills the garden again♪

634
00:39:52,710 --> 00:39:53,490
Zhong Lin.

635
00:39:54,510 --> 00:39:55,820
There is something I have long wanted to ask you.

636
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,490
Why do you treat Ling Cangcang

637
00:39:59,880 --> 00:40:01,130
differently from others?

638
00:40:06,150 --> 00:40:07,940
Perhaps because

639
00:40:08,510 --> 00:40:09,610
from childhood until now,

640
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:13,090
she was the only one who ever wished to protect me.

641
00:40:16,850 --> 00:40:18,100
Where are you taking me?

642
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:19,700
Today is your birthday.

643
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:21,490
I prepared a surprise for you.

644
00:40:23,280 --> 00:40:24,130
Is it beautiful?

645
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:27,050
They say a mountain spirit dwells within this wishing tree.

646
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:28,570
As long as you make a wish,

647
00:40:28,760 --> 00:40:29,740
it will come true.

648
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:30,490
Zhong Lin,

649
00:40:30,510 --> 00:40:31,610
hurry and make a wish.

650
00:40:37,190 --> 00:40:38,650
I know I was wrong.

651
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:41,090
Do not hit me.

652
00:40:49,930 --> 00:40:51,680
Do not hit me.

653
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:14,690
Zhong Lin.

654
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:17,000
I only wanted to give you a surprise.

655
00:41:17,630 --> 00:41:19,130
Forgive me, Zhong Lin.

656
00:41:22,110 --> 00:41:23,010
No, Cangcang.

657
00:41:23,320 --> 00:41:24,610
I should be the one thanking you.

658
00:41:25,190 --> 00:41:25,980
Cangcang.

659
00:41:26,070 --> 00:41:27,490
I want to make a wish.

660
00:41:27,630 --> 00:41:28,210
All right.

661
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:29,090
What is it?

662
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:31,340
I want to be your friend for life,

663
00:41:31,590 --> 00:41:32,780
to treat each other sincerely,

664
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:33,940
never to part.

665
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:34,900
It is a promise.

666
00:41:35,030 --> 00:41:36,980
Then today let us swear sisterhood.

667
00:41:37,230 --> 00:41:38,170
Let this tree bear witness.

668
00:41:38,960 --> 00:41:39,570
Very well.

669
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:43,340
Let the wishing tree bear witness.

670
00:41:43,590 --> 00:41:44,170
Today,

671
00:41:44,550 --> 00:41:45,900
- Ling Cangcang, - Zhong Lin,

672
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:48,490
form a bond of sisterhood.

673
00:41:48,670 --> 00:41:50,170
From this day on,

674
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:53,260
we shall share blessings and hardships alike,

675
00:41:53,710 --> 00:41:55,090
travel the ends of the earth together,

676
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,780
and never betray each other.

677
00:42:00,030 --> 00:42:01,570
From then on,

678
00:42:01,670 --> 00:42:03,380
we became sworn sisters,

679
00:42:03,400 --> 00:42:04,690
inseparable ever since.

680
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:07,940
So she cut down all those bells for you,

681
00:42:08,070 --> 00:42:08,900
without question.

682
00:42:10,070 --> 00:42:10,900
Touched, aren't you?

683
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:13,050
I understand.

684
00:42:27,110 --> 00:42:27,900
Commander Li.

685
00:42:28,320 --> 00:42:29,130
Commander Li.

686
00:42:32,030 --> 00:42:33,820
I saw the dark circles under your eyes lately

687
00:42:33,840 --> 00:42:34,940
and worried you were not sleeping well.

688
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:37,940
So I made this calming sachet for you.

689
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:41,380
It is a small token of my regard.

690
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:42,300
Commander Li,

691
00:42:42,550 --> 00:42:43,820
please accept it.

692
00:42:44,480 --> 00:42:45,490
Do not accept it!

693
00:42:52,920 --> 00:42:53,900
Your Highness.

694
00:43:04,150 --> 00:43:04,940
Your Highness!

695
00:43:31,480 --> 00:43:33,340
Is it because of her that you do not like me?

696
00:43:51,540 --> 00:43:56,380
♪Who walks lone through storm and snow♪

697
00:43:57,300 --> 00:44:00,460
♪Reading every warmth and chill♪

698
00:44:01,420 --> 00:44:04,220
♪Of the heart?♪

699
00:44:06,180 --> 00:44:10,380
♪Who stands proud against a thousand weights♪

700
00:44:11,140 --> 00:44:14,580
♪Grace only a mask he wears?♪

701
00:44:14,820 --> 00:44:17,900
♪My blade sweeps the heavens♪

702
00:44:18,820 --> 00:44:21,340
♪Blood once drenched♪

703
00:44:22,100 --> 00:44:24,820
♪My armor and charging steed♪

704
00:44:25,500 --> 00:44:27,700
♪I know what it means to let go♪

705
00:44:28,620 --> 00:44:32,020
♪When to step in, when to hold back♪

706
00:44:32,460 --> 00:44:35,580
♪A broken blade cuts through♪

707
00:44:35,980 --> 00:44:38,740
♪Years of winter and summer♪

708
00:44:39,620 --> 00:44:41,660
♪Enemy flags burn to ash like gauze♪

709
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:47,700
♪Yet my heart still bears the scars of rise and fall♪

710
00:44:47,860 --> 00:44:53,820
♪I'm willing to wield my sword with you and burn the waning moon♪

711
00:44:55,100 --> 00:45:00,980
♪I'm willing to brave all storms with you, boiling with passion♪

712
00:45:01,780 --> 00:45:07,940
♪I'm willing to break my wings and become the blade in your hand♪

713
00:45:08,740 --> 00:45:14,940
♪I'm willing to write with you this torn, enduring page of history♪

714
00:45:15,860 --> 00:45:21,660
♪I'm willing to travel thousands of miles, seeking your ambition♪

715
00:45:22,900 --> 00:45:28,860
♪I'm willing to give my life to keep you safe for a lifetime♪

716
00:45:29,700 --> 00:45:36,220
♪I'm willing to sing through every farewell and wait for you another thousand years♪

717
00:45:36,660 --> 00:45:44,100
♪I'm willing to live and die with you, my one and only wish in this lifetime♪

